data.eml:eml: Two new subspecies of the leaf-tailed gecko Phyllurus ossa (Lacertilia: Carphodactylidae) from mid-eastern Queensland, Australia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Couper, Patrick, Hoskin, Conrad J. (2013): Two new subspecies of the leaf-tailed gecko Phyllurus ossa (Lacertilia: Carphodactylidae) from mid-eastern Queensland, Australia. Zootaxa 3664 (4): 537-553, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3664.4.7
